  "description": {
    "zh": "感谢你帮我弄好那把M4，真的是帮了大忙。不巧的是，那位雇佣兵再也没有支付尾款。我是因为老熟人才选择相信他的，可是他一拿到武器就冲进了实验室，至今杳无音讯。我估计是他太贪了... 总之，我之后需要解决这件事情，不过现在我有别的想法。我正在收集我服务相关的反馈信息，寻找新的业务方向，你明白吗？我决定了，不仅要接个人订单，还要批量销售枪械，成箱成箱地卖。测试一下它们，你也可以找你的同行们帮帮忙。每一个小点都至关重要！记得多检查检查武器，我觉得你是明白怎么操作的...",
    "en": "Thanks for the help with the M4, you really helped me out. Unfortunately, this mercenary never transferred the payment he promised me. I trusted him because of old acquaintances, but the guy went straight to the lab as soon as he received the weapon, and so far there is no word from him. Got too greedy, that's my guess... Well anyway, I can deal with this matter later, but I also have something else on my mind.\nI'm collecting feedback on my services, looking for a fresh perspective, you know? I've decided not only to do individual orders, but to sell guns in sets, fully loaded out of the box. Test it out properly, ask your colleagues maybe. Every little detail and view point is important! And be sure to check the weapons in action, I'm sure you know how...."
  },
